 \left(\frac{1}{2}\right)^{\lg n} = \frac{1^{\lg n}}{2^{\lg n}} = \frac{1}{2^{\lg n}} = \frac{1}{n} 
2^{\lg n} = n
2^{\lg n} = \left(e^{\log 2}\right)^{\lg n} = \left(e^{\log 2}\right)^{\log(n)/\log(2)} = e^{\log n} = n
